<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hr">
<head>
    <%- include('../modules/head', { pageTitle: 'Dobrodošli', device: device }) %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../modules/header', { lang: 'hr', base: '/hr/desktop' }) %>
    <main>
        <section class="hero glassy">
            <h1>Dobrodošli u Apartmane Šibenik</h1>
            <p>Uživajte u modernom smještaju uz more, s predivnim pogledom, vrhunskom udobnošću i autentičnim doživljajem Dalmacije. Naša ponuda uključuje apartman s vrtom, studio apartman i sobu, idealno za obitelji, parove i solo putnike.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="gallery-preview glassy">
            <h2>Galerija</h2>
            <%- include('../modules/gallery', { images: [
                { fullsize: '/images/gallery/apartment/veliki-slike-01.jpg', thumbnail: '/images/gallery/apartment/veliki-slike-01.jpg', alt: 'Apartman s vrtom' },
                { fullsize: '/images/gallery/studio/veliki-slike-01.jpg', thumbnail: '/images/gallery/studio/veliki-slike-01.jpg', alt: 'Studio apartman' },
                { fullsize: '/images/gallery/room/veliki-slike-01.jpg', thumbnail: '/images/gallery/room/veliki-slike-01.jpg', alt: 'Soba' },
                { fullsize: '/images/gallery/sibenik/veliki-slike-01.jpg', thumbnail: '/images/gallery/sibenik/veliki-slike-01.jpg', alt: 'Šibenik' }
            ] }) %>
        </section>
        <section class="about glassy">
            <h2>Zašto odabrati nas?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Lokacija uz more i blizina centra Šibenika</li>
                <li>Moderno uređeni apartmani i sobe</li>
                <li>Privatni vrt i terasa</li>
                <li>Besplatan Wi-Fi i parking</li>
                <li>Ljubazni domaćini i autentično dalmatinsko iskustvo</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../modules/footer') %>
    <script src="/javascripts/header.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Dinamička promjena pozadine ovisno o dobu dana
        function setDynamicBackground() {
            const hour = new Date().getHours();
            let bg;
            if (hour >= 20 || hour < 6) {
                bg = 'var(--night-bg)';
            } else if (hour >= 6 && hour < 18) {
                bg = 'var(--day-bg)';
            } else {
                bg = 'var(--evening-bg)';
            }
            document.body.style.background = bg;
        }
        setDynamicBackground();
    </script>
</body>
</html>